verses.1: Amah hoih ahih manin Topa tungah lungdamna ko un; bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
verses.2: Lungdamna pen pasian-teʼ Pasianʼ tungah ko un; bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
verses.3: Lungdamna pen topateʼ Topaʼ tungah ko un; bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
verses.4: Nalamdang lian a bawl amah bek Pasian ahi paʼ tungah, bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
verses.5: Theihna tawh vantungte a bawlpa tungah, bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
verses.6: Tuite tungah leitung a zal pa tungah, bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
verses.7: Khuavak lianpite a bawlpa tungah, bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
verses.8: Sun pen ni a uksak pa tungah, bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
verses.9: Zan pen kha le aksite a uksak pa tungah, bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
verses.10: Egypt gam tacil khempeuh a vatmaipa tungah, bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
verses.11: Amauʼ gam sung pan Israel-te a paikhiatpih pa tungah, bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
verses.12: A baan zanin a khut thahat tawh a paikhiatpih pa tungah, bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
verses.13: San Tuipi a phel kham pa tungah, bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
verses.14: Israel-te tui laizang a kantan sakpa tungah, bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
verses.15: Ahih hangin Faro le a mihonte San Tuipi sungah a thal paih pa tungah, bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
verses.16: Sehnel gam nawkin ama mite a paipih pa tungah, bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
verses.17: Kumpi liante a vatmaipa tungah, bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
verses.18: Kumpi minthangte a that pa tungah, bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
verses.19: Amor miteʼ kumpipa Sihonʼ hang le, bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi;
verses.20: Bashan kumpipa Ogʼ hangin, bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
verses.21: Amauteʼ leitang pen gamhluah dingin a pia khia pa tungah, bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
verses.22: Ama nasem Israel tungah gamh a a pia pa tungah, bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
verses.23: Mi niam ihih laitakin a hong phawk pa tungah, bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
verses.24: I galteʼ kiang pan eite hong hon khia pa tungah, bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
verses.25: Nuntakna a nei khempeuh an a vak pa tungah, bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
verses.26: Vantung Pasianʼ tungah lungdamna ko un; bang hang hiam cih leh ama itna kip tawntung hi.
